page.title: 09A Day in the Life of Jo
page.content: I woke up at 7.30am and got up at 8.00.I then went downstairs for breakfast.I had a shower and went to school with Charlotte Lewis at 8.45.At school I did{English Comprehension}and {Maths,}then we had a service with Mr. Beale.We went out to play at 10.40,I played {cricket}on the school field. I had a{school dinner}at 12.00 and I played cricket again until we went back into school.I painted a picture about a computer adventure and then the whole class played stoolball. I went home at 3.25 and I had to go to Fiona's party,it was a disco.I got back at 7.00.I watched T.V. and went to bed at 9.30.
